title: The computer or the launcher?
body: I already started 2 lol games and the load page didnt work on both, i lost my ranked points and now i have leaverbuster, i just want to know if its my computer who is doing this or if is the launcher... cause i dont want to play and keep losing points :l

replies.body: Can you offer me a bit more detail in regards to what specific behaviour you saw when you weren't able to load into a match? Did you see any specific error messages when this happened?
Its okay now, and sorry for not answering, i really dont know, its probably just my computer, if something like this happens again i will post again, thanks :P
